    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越多个星系，收集非法货物，在危险区域中运送——同时还要躲避太空警察的追捕。在《Rogue Run》中，每一笔交易都是对时间与法律的赛跑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292110/extras/dc589cf37db580c76bf827de4285084c.poster.avif?t=1764089082\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292110/extras/dc589cf37db580c76bf827de4285084c.webm?t=1764089082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292110/extras/dc589cf37db580c76bf827de4285084c.mp4?t=1764089082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🚀 运送为先</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目标简单：<strong>15分钟内完成至少100笔走私交付</strong>。活下来，<strong>行动基地会来救你</strong>，带上你的战利品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292110/extras/6ae2a7950fb89ec680cdf40ab99662c0.poster.avif?t=1764089082\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292110/extras/6ae2a7950fb89ec680cdf40ab99662c0.webm?t=1764089082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292110/extras/6ae2a7950fb89ec680cdf40ab99662c0.mp4?t=1764089082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💥 <strong>开火吧</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在比赛中获取强力的临时武器，狠狠教训那些家伙，别让他们抓到你。至少暂时如此。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔧 星际工坊</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从<strong>数十种升级选项中挑选</strong>，每局都独一无二。<strong>在神秘的Black先生的移动工坊中强化飞船</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292110/extras/7f5a83f2042e025d1629723108d2b7aa.poster.avif?t=1764089082\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292110/extras/7f5a83f2042e025d1629723108d2b7aa.webm?t=1764089082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292110/extras/7f5a83f2042e025d1629723108d2b7aa.mp4?t=1764089082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🛸 飞船多样性</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁并升级不同飞船，每艘都有<strong>独特属性与技能</strong>，<strong>适应多种玩法风格</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292110/extras/86c9081dc1ac8b8d446fa1db0b47d584.poster.avif?t=1764089082\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292110/extras/86c9081dc1ac8b8d446fa1db0b47d584.webm?t=1764089082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292110/extras/86c9081dc1ac8b8d446fa1db0b47d584.mp4?t=1764089082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚠️ 动态通缉等级</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成交付越多，<strong>通缉等级越高</strong>，将吸引<strong>更快、更强、更狠的敌人</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏆 分数与排行榜</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过<strong>街机式排名系统</strong>与其他玩家间接竞争。<strong>谁送得多，谁就说了算</strong>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292110/extras/fbed3b84f2c1372ae314aff53b9edd19.poster.avif?t=1764089082\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292110/extras/fbed3b84f2c1372ae314aff53b9edd19.webm?t=1764089082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292110/extras/fbed3b84f2c1372ae314aff53b9edd19.mp4?t=1764089082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌌 随机宇宙事件</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>黑洞、太阳风暴、星云</strong>等宇宙现象将随机出现，<strong>直接影响游戏进程</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>做好准备</strong>，<strong>挑战宇宙极限</strong>，<strong>用策略、反应与风险掌控</strong>，成为<strong>银河最臭名昭著的走私者</strong>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292110/extras/6fd944c8d49a42c3aee955dad8cafa06.poster.avif?t=1764089082\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292110/extras/6fd944c8d49a42c3aee955dad8cafa06.webm?t=1764089082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292110/extras/6fd944c8d49a42c3aee955dad8cafa06.mp4?t=1764089082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
